# RAG Book Question-Answering System

A Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) system for intelligent book analysis and question answering, built with Flask and OpenAI.

## Features

- Upload and process various document formats (PDF, DOCX, TXT, ODT)
- Real-time processing progress updates via WebSocket
- Intelligent question answering using OpenAI's GPT models
- Vector-based document search using Pinecone
- Caching system for embeddings and responses
- Web interface with Markdown support for responses

## Technical Stack

- **Backend**: Flask, Flask-SocketIO
- **AI/ML**: OpenAI API, Pinecone
- **Document Processing**: PyPDF, python-docx, odfpy
- **Text Processing**: NLTK, spaCy
- **Frontend**: jQuery, Marked.js, Font Awesome

